Application under test : htp://zero.webappsecurity.com/
Login credentials:
Username = “username”
Password = “password”

Login Feature
    - Only authorized users should be able to login to the application. [DONE]
    - When user logs in with valid credentials, Account summary page should be displayed. [DONE]
    - Users with wrong username or wrong password should not be able to login. [DONE]
    - Users with blank username or password should also not be able to login. [DONE]
    - When user tries to login with invalid information, error message “Login and/or password are wrong.” should be displayed.[DONE]

Account summary Feature
    - Account summary page should have the title Zero – Account summary.
    - Account summary page should have to following account types:
    --- Cash Accounts,
    --- Investment Accounts,
    --- Credit Accounts,
    ----- Credit Accounts table must have columns
    -------- Account,
    -------- Credit Card,
    -------- Balance.
    --- Loan Accounts.

Account Activity Feature
    - Account Activity page should have the title Zero – Account activity.
    - In the Account drop down default option should be Savings.
    - Account drop down should have the following options:
    --- Savings,
    --- Checking,
    --- Loan,
    --- Credit Card,
    --- Brokerage.
    - Transactions table should have column names;
    --- Date,
    --- Description,
    --- Deposit,
    --- Withdrawal.